  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.2.3">
<l>vempum ciṉattup puṉakkē ḻaloṉṟāy virinīr mutuveḷ ḷamuḷpuk kaḻunta</l>
<l>vampuṇ poḻilcū ḻulakaṉ ṟeṭuttā ṉaṭippō taṇaivāṉ viruppō ṭiruppīr</l>
<l>paimpoṉ ṉumuttum maṇiyuṅ koṇarntu paṭaimaṉ ṉavaṉpal lavarkkōṉ paṇinta</l>
<l>cempoṉ maṇimā ṭaṅkaḷcūḻn tatillait tiruccit rakūṭam ceṉṟucēr miṉkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who are with longing to embrace the bud[-like] feet of him</l>
<l rend="indent">who, as a forest boar with a fury that burned,</l>
<l>When he plunged entering into the ancient flood of spreading waters</l>
<l rend="indent">that day, took up the earth encircled by forests under the sea,</l>
<l>Go and gather at Tiruccitrakūṭam in Tillai, surrounded by mansions</l>
<l rend="indent">with rose gold and jewels,</l>
<l>Where worshipped the king of the Pallavas, leader of the army,</l>
<l rend="indent">bringing bright gold, pearls, and jewels.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
